des:
Listen to this interactive story with a timeless lesson. 
Here is a puzzle, who lives outdoors most of the time, begs for food from strangers and can share your bed and home? The answer is the feral cat!, listen on to discover the feral cat in you, as you play an interactive story of a cat you name. 
At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
